WEBVTT

00:03.570 --> 00:07.670
Captain Rogers, you were meant to be the first super soldier.

00:08.640 --> 00:11.110
You're stronger, faster,...

00:11.710 --> 00:14.680
...and better equipped for combat than any human alive.

00:15.810 --> 00:19.010
And we have given you these gifts for one reason:...

00:19.610 --> 00:22.280
...you will crush Red Skull and his army...

00:22.580 --> 00:24.620
...by any means necessary.

